‘Deep End’ is out today, available everywhere you listen to music. 
.
.
It’s the first song off my new project, and is dedicated to everyone fighting invisible battles that no one else can see. The ‘deep end’ is a place we’ve all been to before for any number of reasons, where you feel like you’re fighting to stay afloat, and it’s a fight for every breathe, and that’s just how powerful certain negative experiences in our lives, minds and hearts can affect us. We’ll talk a lot more about it. 
.
.
But for now, please listen, share it, stream it, save it in your library, make a crazy TikTok to it, do anything that feels right! 
.
.

The more authentic you are to yourself, the less people you will please. The right people will be attracted to you, the wrong people will be repulsed, and that’s fine, as you shouldn’t aim to please everyone. Certainly, playing it safe and being a chameleon is smart in certain situations, but being a bold individual, living confidently in your energy and having a ‘take it or leave it’ attitude is a more noble lifestyle choice. 
.
.
As an artist and creative, I learned this lesson early on in life, and many people have lost me because I wouldn’t adapt my energy to match theirs, or compromise my goals to appease their egos. Many others simply never understand me to begin with because they can’t relate, and I’m cool with that too.
.
.
I have always been the lone wolf, making my own path, speaking my own language, and depending on no one to fulfill my identity, purpose, or meaning in life. This is the sole reason why at this point, my mentality is bulletproof and my opinion of myself is immovable no matter what people say, think, or do about me. 
.
.
Just continue being yourself and never compromise to keep people in your life, let them let you go if they can’t handle or appreciate who you are, the right people are out there that will. This life is YOUR journey, your purpose is YOURS to fulfill, no one can complete you, YOU have to complete you. 
.
.
.
.
#wordofwisdom #philosophy #philosophical #philosophers #wisdomquote #wednesdaywisdom #innerwisdom #wordsofwisdom #wisdomoftheday #wisewords #wise #lifeadvice #adviceoftheday #deepthoughts #thoughtsoftheday #thoughtsforlife #positivethoughts

.
.
.
